Map Info: mg_dance_or_die By ZaLoS This is DDR(dance dance revolution) for css. I made this DDR machine myself, completely from scratch. Dance! Dance! Dance! If you miss a step you take damage! All steps except the warmup round were custom made by me. (warmup round steps are generated at random) After about 2mins of dance battling youll be transported to the arena with a random weapon to finish each other off. Have fun!
How it works: The black screen contains the upcoming steps. The arrows immediately infront of you indicate which arrows you have recently pressed. When they turn blue you are pressing them. You have to stop pressing a button to press it again, you cant just stand on a button! When the black screen arrows change colors you are suppose to hit your own arrow in response, if you dont you get hurt! Each songs steps last about 2mins, at the end the winners are transported to the arena and given a random weapon or just knife fight.. This will be challenging at first till you get the hang of it! keep at it!

This is a smaller project i've been working on for quite a while now, it's based out of mariokart with some of my own tweaks. I felt like it's time to release it as it is now. This map has these features:

  • Driveable karts, first person style!
  • 32 players max / karts avalible
  • 11 different items you can use (basic mariokart items)
  • Random coloring for the karts
  • 4 different stages (will add more in the future!)
  • 3 playable modes (race, battle and star battle)
  • Winning system! The winner gets to choose stage next round
  • Particle effects
  • custom materials, textures and models made by myself
  • Slow motion events, during some occasions
  • Players actually die, with exploding karts falling apart in flames and smoke!

EDIT V1_1

  • Edited the length of some soundtracks in order for the "Fair Act Use"

KNOWN ISSUES

  • Delayed controls, nothing can really be done about that. It's the game_ui (the entity which you can control the kart with)

  • Karts tend to steer away by their own (just slightly) As you play you will eventually learn how to overcome it and use it at your disposal. This can't really be fixed either since it's a physic bug.

  • Lag spikes on some servers with many players (due to high amounts of IN, caused by all the game_ui's working at the same time) This seems to differ between servers aswell, depending on some settings. This might stop my plans for making players invincible during 1st lap and adding 8 more karts. We'll see how things turns out.

FUTURE PLANS

  • I might add some extra karts, since alot of people have been asking for 40 karts in total. This might however become a risk for crashing. We'll see how it turns out.

  • I will add more stages such as a ice/snow stage, rainbow road, bowsers castle and maybe some crazy industrial stage.

  • As things are now, i have an ongoing project already (and quite a big one at that) so i wont fully concentrate on updating this map, i'll do things in my own speed.

  • I think i will make the players/karts invincible for the first lap on the race courses, i've gotten complaints about players dying too early. We'll see how it turns out.

NEXT VERSION

  • MORE STAGES! snowland, bowsers castle and rainbow road planned. Might add more on top of that.
  • SWEET FIXES! no more star exploiting, flying or karts with 2 players in it
  • BALANCE TWEAKS! nerfed items, less unfairness, less rage, no exploitable shortcuts
  • MORE FUN! maybe some new items, player pickable models at start, different kart models, score-based progress for each stage

A mini game where you spawn with a knife and a target box and you try to eliminate the other team using teleports. Aim your box onto an enemy or a friendly then right click with your knife and it will teleport them in front of you. You can use this system very tactically to gang up or snatch weak enemies, or you can use it to save your teammates out of a fight they are going to loose. Many different tactics are possible using this teleport system and experience with it does matter. Its a lot of fun if you know how to use it. [REMEMBER Right Click to teleport anyone touching your target zone] Set up for 10v10. Please comment on how the game play is and rate it if you enjoy the map. Thanks to Tran for testing the map with me.

Once you beat all three levels, you will be in a room saying "Congrats!" with 3 buttons below the sigh. Every time you beat the map you get to choose one button. Each button will tell you a huge hint on finding a secret button within the map (1 secret button for each level). this is a mg running map for counter strike source based on lara croft tomb raider revelations. its in beta mode at the moment and currently only holds 12 players. it is fun and enjoyable and i hope you like it. added 24 player slots

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ts

Objective: Protect the town.

Brief: Recently a patch of petroleum was found in the field north west of the farm house. The government wanted to build an oil rig in our own backyards and intended to kicks us out. Fortunately the Supreme Court overruled and decided not to. Government officials were not happy. We figured theyre after the oil, and want to waste us, so grab your guns, and any explosives you have. Not sure whos attacking us, but they want our town, defend it at all costs.

CTs

Objective: Take out the civilians as quickly as possible.

Brief: A small town in Texas is giving us a bit of trouble, we found oil, but the Supreme Court overruled its extraction, too many folks would be homeless. We are going to fix that problem. Ive collected the best in the military for the job; you have all been trained in special ops and stealth, so I expect perfection. Youll have limited ammo, KM .45 Tactical (USP), two smoke and flash grenades, and your average combat knife. A new suit has arrived and you boys will test driving it, youll be stronger and able to jump higher. This should be a piece of cake, good luck, and God speed!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

HINT: CT's health will only regenerate if it gets below 100.
